data.description: Seize the chance to own a lucrative investment in this modern duplex comprising two units, each commanding a rent of $2,500 or higher.  this property presents an exceptional opportunity for both steady rental income and Airbnb possibilities. These city homes offer the comfort of single-family living with a distinct advantage—an exclusive fenced-in yard and no HOA constraints, ensuring privacy and autonomy. Step inside to discover an intelligently designed layout, starting with an inviting enclosed study—ideal for a home office—complemented by three additional bedrooms upstairs.The heart of each unit reveals an open-concept design, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen exudes elegance with light cabinets, quartz countertops, and a spacious walk-in pantry. A substantial counter-height island becomes the focal point, ideal for family gatherings or hosting memorable cocktail parties. Connected seamlessly to the kitchen, the family room boasts a stunning wall of windows that beckons natural light and offers picturesque views of the expansive patio and a sprawling yard spanning almost 40 feet from the lanai to the garage.The oversized owner's retreat stands as a testament to comfort, featuring a tray ceiling and ample natural light. The en-suite bathroom impresses with a walk-in shower sporting a frameless glass enclosure, private water closet, double vanities, and a generously sized walk-in closet.Attention to detail elevates this property, evident in its features like impact glass windows and doors, flush mount LED lights, a meticulously painted garage floor with anti-skid flakes, and exquisite backsplash tiles in the kitchen. Notably, niches in the shower add a touch of functionality and charm.A one-year warranty underscores the confidence in the quality of this home, providing peace of mind to the new owner. Don't miss this opportunity to own a property that harmonizes efficiency, beauty, and comfort—a place to truly call home.
